## Segment 1: 00:00.933 => 00:20.533
The video showcases a series of tech products on a desk. It begins with a Surface Laptop Studio, prominently displayed with a watch placed in front of it. The scene then shifts to a Dell 34-inch monitor, followed by a close-up of a Logitech mouse on a mouse pad. Next, a pair of Pose headphones is shown on the desk. Finally, the video highlights a set of box speakers placed on a shelf above the monitor.
